{"id":"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05","title":"第5课：向组件添加输入参数","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"lesson-5-add-an-input-parameter-to-the-component\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1z871gsai5ab8jckkwb9nuhhv\">第5课：向组件添加输入参数<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#lesson-5-add-an-input-parameter-to-the-component\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3p70196w9godwtwzrzg7wo0p3\">本教程演示了如何创建一个组件\n<code>@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</code>，并将其用于向组件传递数据以进行自定义。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9b0304m4wmxslkazn9h6yr4kn\"><strong>预计时间</strong>: 约10分钟</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"96hsnd9pb5jdi4pzovf3sggb9\"><strong>初始代码：</strong> \n<live-example name=\"first-app-lesson-04\"></live-example></p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8r4xaz157a51ute0xgwd68x3k\"><strong>完成的代码：</strong> \n<live-example name=\"first-app-lesson-05\"></live-example></p>\n<h2 id=\"what-youll-learn\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cy8qhuh22qozu5okjmjfdf3nx\">你将学到<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#what-youll-learn\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dznk2i7zxx9054q4wgbmoqg51\">你的应用的\n<code>HousingLocationComponent</code>模板具有一个\n<code>HousingLocation</code>属性来接收输入。</p>\n<h2 id=\"conceptual-preview-of-inputs\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eeam3k169tsbsub1gv24k6e72\">输入属性的概念性预览<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#conceptual-preview-of-inputs\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"exwsnl347w76jo7z8pok8vdgg\"><a href=\"api/core/Input\">输入属性</a>允许组件共享数据。数据共享的方向是从父组件到子组件。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"442eg1z84zo62wsb7mty5em37\">在这节课中，你将在 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code> 组件中定义 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</code> 属性，这能让你自定义要在组件中显示的数据。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1konigui0j0p421kv5rsdq3wr\">在\n<a href=\"guide/inputs-outputs\">在子指令和组件之间共享数据</a>指南中了解更多信息。</p>\n<h2 id=\"step-1---import-the-input-decorator\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"amg3xuf3alu7fx57a3x4j2jrm\">第 1 步 - 导入 <code><a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a></code> 装饰器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#step-1---import-the-input-decorator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2nx582j1qd95psiiek6fbh9h8\">此步骤将 <code><a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a></code> 装饰器导入到类中。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eug3k0hymd4usfrh9oohvkiee\">在代码编辑器中：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2j1hhdzuzpzh4rxn5ms2fbmah\">导航到 <code>src/app/housing-location/housing-location.component.ts</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a4cn2zwhjxuid24ahfaf0cmbw\">更新文件的导入代码以包含 <code><a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a></code> 和 <code>HousingLocation</code>：</p>\n<code-example header=\"Import HousingLocationComponent and Input in src/app/housing-location/housing-location.component.ts\" path=\"first-app-lesson-05/src/app/housing-location/housing-location.component.ts\" region=\"add-imports\">\nimport { <a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a> } from '@angular/core';\nimport { <a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">CommonModule</a> } from '@angular/common';\nimport { HousingLocation } from '../housinglocation';\n\n</code-example>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"step-2---add-the-input-property\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dnixn54jf01xg4ffxj7npuxei\">第 2 步 - 添加输入属性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#step-2---add-the-input-property\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9vtesq23zq7j491drqz6hjof3\">在同一个文件中，名为 <code>housingLocation</code> 的 <code>HousingLocation</code> 型属性添加到 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code> 类。在属性名之后添加一个 <code>!</code> 并在它前面加上 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</code> 装饰器：</p>\n<code-example header=\"Import HousingLocationComponent and Input in src/app/housing-location/housing-location.component.ts\" path=\"first-app-lesson-05/src/app/housing-location/housing-location.component.ts\" region=\"add-housing-location-property\">\nexport class HousingLocationComponent {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>() housingLocation!: HousingLocation;\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"exnwwjcumhn66uc10et5oh3qo\">你必须加上 <code>!</code>，是因为这个输入属性期望有传入值。在这种情况下，没有合适的默认值。在这个示例应用程序中，我们就知道必须传入该值 —— 设计意图就是如此。感叹号称为非空断言运算符，它告诉 TypeScript 编译器此属性的值不能是 <code>null</code> 或 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6a1306fc3w56aeqm1wcmz5ewr\">保存你的更改并确认应用程序没有任何错误。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2kcshog2nszydh73ast6suqu6\">在继续下一步之前更正所有错误。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"lesson-review\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ckmo8mg671uh3oxv2z72tuj64\">课程回顾<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#lesson-review\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"920zt69jo4q1z0hb9a2vu91d9\">在这节课中，你创建了一个用 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</code> 装饰器装饰的新属性。还使用了非空断言运算符来通知编译器新属性的值不能是 <code>null</code> 或 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2vi4aou9du2w1ijyabax7x8qx\">如果你在学习这节课时遇到了任何问题，可以在<live-example></live-example>查看完整代码。</p>\n<h2 id=\"next-steps\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c4pkljueu68ifjoi5994e9l8o\">下一步<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#next-steps\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"153hhwgq21pv9w0tsse794c1i\"><a href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06\">第 6 课 - 将属性绑定添加到组件的模板中</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ep5mlw3d5q1ucm62jzem9a7pc\">有关这节课中涵盖的主题的更多信息，请访问：<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"u8onr681o2pvtu7uifsr3r82\"><a href=\"guide/inputs-outputs\">在子指令与父指令和组件之间共享数据</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间：Tue Jul 11 2023</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-04\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Input\n - guide/inputs-outputs\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#conceptual-preview-of-inputs\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#lesson-5-add-an-input-parameter-to-the-component\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#lesson-review\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#next-steps\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#step-1---import-the-input-decorator\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#step-2---add-the-input-property\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05#what-youll-learn\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06\n-->"}